name: LyricsTrivia
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lyrics trivia
des: This skill will test how well you know popular song lyrics. When you say "Alexa, play lyrics trivia," Alexa will give you five questions in which you must complete the song lyrics with the correct answer choice from a list she gives you. Try to get all of them right!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
